{"tid":933124,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白宮爆炸 白宮又爆炸 格林雙俠 白事可樂","createTime":"2018-12-08T09:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T19:50:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb43466822e79b876c2f68c7692d94f6564e2f7","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=123fede2\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8400a07b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e93bbbe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/Olympus_Has_Fallen_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FOlympus_Has_Fallen_poster.jpg&h=511003d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/5d/White_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F5d%2FWhite_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg&h=0de00aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7a/Hansel_and_Gretel-_Witch_Hunters_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7a%2FHansel_and_Gretel-_Witch_Hunters_Poster.jpg&h=61ccf1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9f/Newworldwarzpostersmall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9f%2FNewworldwarzpostersmall.jpg&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.麥克&middot;班寧是從美國陸軍遊騎兵退役的美國特勤局隊員，負責保護美國總統班傑明&middot;埃舍。一次聖誕節前夕，埃舍跟妻子瑪姬和兒子康納到大衛營度假折返時，在一座橋上因雪天路滑導致車禍，總統轎車剛好被卡在橋邊上並開始下墜。因情況急迫，班寧只將埃舍拽出汽車，第一夫人跟著汽車掉下橋梁墜亡。事後，埃舍和康納父子倆處於長時間的悲痛期，班寧也因為此事造成難以抹去的心理陰影，於是退出特勤隊調至美國財政部的保全工作。十八個月後，美國獨立日隔天，班寧從他的老友兼特勤局主任蓮恩&middot;傑克布斯得知，埃舍今日要和到訪的韓國總理討論朝鮮核問題<br />\n<br />\n2.宣揚和平主義的美國總統詹姆士&middot;索耶爲了結束長久以來的中東戰爭而親自前往伊朗表示和平，聲言他會把所有部署在中東地區的美軍全部撤出，將自己的提案交給其他國家審核。約翰&middot;凱爾是一名在阿富汗服過兵役的美軍中士，因爲行爲不檢被革除後去當國會警察，成為美國眾議院議長伊萊&middot;拉弗森的私人護衛。而約翰好不容易得到一次美國特勤局的面試機會，並與自己關係不好的女兒愛蜜莉一同前去白宮。面試時，特勤隊副主任卡蘿&middot;菲妮提因為看不上約翰的狼藉簡歷而拒絕了他<br />\n<br />\n3.構思自家喻戶曉的格林童話「糖果屋」。「糖果屋」故事發生後的15年，韓賽爾與葛蕾特這對兄妹成為了所向無敵的獎金獵人，專門消滅世界各地的女巫<br />\n<br />\n4.前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f7eea0ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=41d7da53\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4821b863aed91b8735240927c86ba7bd8a6e2938","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dec4a00280ecba04a380065612e3b5eb3fa7a81","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775deefff26d97a991b610a7a60fcd84cbcb22fa","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46130a428707d339e43c288ef4eaf947ea44cd1","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d661310704fc279d5659044927520b96bcf171e9","tid":933124,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma